description:
This high level map of the ESnet 5 network highlights the sites ESnet serves, the structure of the network and the current traffic load. More information about each node and edge on the map is available by clicking on that node or edge.

In order to increase the legibility of this map two simplifications have been systematically applied. The first simplification is that connectivity for each site is shown as a single pair of lines which show the traffic traversing all connections to the site. This simplification means that this map does not show the fault tolerence which has been carefully engineered to provide the sites with highly available connectivity. An additional map is under development which will show this fault tolerence at some cost to legibility. The second simplification is that for any pair of nodes shown there is only a single pair of lines representing all of the connections between that pair of nodes.
